&lt;li&gt;Pursue government and prime-contractor subcontracting opportunities for the company&#39;s special-mission integration capabilities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and vet local partnerships, sub-tier vendors, and expansion opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
