&lt;p&gt;Every dollar of revenue we generate removes two dollars from the healthcare system. If we succeed, so does US&lt;br&gt;healthcare.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our platform operates at materially higher gross margins than traditional home health providers. We pay clinicians&lt;br&gt;more, strip out their admin burden, and unlock scale economics that have eluded this fragmented industry for decades.&lt;br&gt;We are backed by world-class investors — Felicis, Bain Capital Ventures, BoxGroup, and Optum Ventures — and&lt;br&gt;scaling nationally through organic growth and acquisition.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;THE OPPORTUNITY&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are hiring General Managers to own and operate individual markets as we scale nationally. This is a P&amp;amp;L&lt;br&gt;ownership role. You will run your market — a metropolitan area or MSA — as your own business. You own the&lt;br&gt;census, the margin, the team, the clinical quality, and the growth trajectory.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Some GMs will take over existing operations and transform them. Others will stand up new markets from scratch,&lt;br&gt;including post-acquisition integrations. All will operate with the intensity, ownership, and judgment of a founder running&lt;br&gt;a business backed by a growth-stage platform and top-tier investors. All GMs receive a robust onboarding program to&lt;br&gt;learn the industry and the business before stepping into the seat.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT THE GM OWNS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Market P&amp;amp;L&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;• Full accountability for revenue, census growth, gross margin, and unit economics&lt;br&gt;• Drive census growth in partnership with Sales — translate referral pipeline into admitted, scheduled, and served&lt;br&gt;patients&lt;br&gt;• Leverage data and AI-driven tooling for daily resource allocation decisions that convert top-line growth into&lt;br&gt;bottom-line results&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Operations&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br&gt;• Run daily execution across scheduling, staffing, clinical compliance, and service delivery&lt;br&gt;• Single point of accountability for compliance, survey readiness, and clinical quality in your market&lt;br&gt;• Partner cross-functionally with centralized Technology, Compliance, and Operations — you own local outcomes&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Team&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br&gt;• Hire, develop, and lead your market&#39;s operations team — Schedulers, Patient Care Coordinators, Clinical&lt;br&gt;Managers, Sales Reps, and field clinicians&lt;br&gt;• Build bench strength ahead of volume; sequence hiring and training to support growth, not just maintain current&amp;nbsp;operations&lt;br&gt;• Set clear expectations, coach through structured routines, and make the hard calls on performance&lt;/p&gt;
